title: LOL - Sydney LAN Tournament - eLeauge.gg

embed.description: NAVIGATION " Events > eLeague Autumn BYOC 2016 > LoL eSports Competition

body:
Hi All,

We have a LOL competition coming up on the 19th March in Sydney hosted by eLeague.gg.

$1,000 for first and $500 for second, including RP prizes, IP boosts and the Triumphant Ryze skin for the 1st place team.

Limited to 8 teams and run in double elimination, sign ups will open soon and will need to be done pre-event at www.ELEAGUE.gg.

This event is sponsored by ASUS and NVIDIA, with giveaway prizes to the first 100 ticket sales and also to one person who is 'attending' on the Facebook event.

More info and announcements: 
https://www.facebook.com/events/444336562440304/
https://eleague.gg/events/1/page/3
